metadata.name: HER GENESIS  #1/50
metadata.description:
Beyond the lies  
Of diamond blinds  
Silvered tongues  
And shattered lives  
The artist strives,  
She bides her time,  
In love and war  
Fine Art Survives.    

HER GENESIS TOKEN holders are guaranteed pre-mint listed 
for the upcoming "HER RAYS" Collection featuring : 100 original 1/1 artworks dedicated to French Man-Ray model and artist, Kiki de Montparnasse, who died homeless in Paris at fifty-one years old.
